The '''Forad Party''' was a political party on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Esseles/Legends|Esseles]]. During the height of the [[New Order/Legends|New Order]], it was known for its tolerance of [[Alien/Legends|nonhumans]] and its advocacy for assuming greater power from [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[Governor/Legends|Governor]] [[Griff Takel]]. It was opposed by the [[Cardean Party|Cardean]] and [[Esselian New Order Party|Esselian New Order Parties]]. [[Esselian Hall|Hall]] [[President/Legends|President]] [[Cambira Ralle]] was a member of the Forad Party.

Following the [[Esselian Hall election, 2 ABY|election]] of [[2 ABY/Legends|2 ABY]], the Forad Party lost its grip on the majority, with the Esselian New Order Party making major inroads.

